Package com.netflix.spectator.tdigest

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TDigestReader
    Reader for consuming T-Digest measurements.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileTDigestReader
    Reader for measurements stored in a file.
    FileTDigestWriter
    Write measurements to a file.
    KinesisTDigestReader
    Reader to consume data from a single shard of a Kinesis stream.
    KinesisTDigestWriter
    Writer that sends the measurements to a Kinesis stream.
    StreamTDigestReader
    Reader based on an underlying InputStream.
    StreamTDigestWriter
    Write measurements to an output stream.
    TDigestConfig
    Configuration settings for the digest plugin.
    TDigestMeasurement
    A measurement sampled from a meter.
    TDigestModule Deprecated
    Use PercentileTimer instead.
    TDigestRegistry Deprecated
    Use PercentileTimer instead.
    TDigestTestModule
    Guice module to configure the plugin.
